title: Houari Boumediene International Airport (DAAG) now available for MSFS!
description:
An updated facility for Algiers, Houari Boumediene International Airport (DAAG), also referred to as Algiers Airport or Algiers International Airport, serves as the primary international gateway to Algiers. Those wishing to travel to Algiers now have access to this modernized airport.
